    "description": "猫咪的生活从未如此忙碌过！在 &quot;9 Lives to Defend&quot; 中，您将扮演洛基的角色，他是一只勇敢的猫，在他的父母外出旅行时需要保卫家园免受入侵者侵害。仅有九条生命，您的生存能力将在疯狂的子弹地狱中受到考验，面对成群结队的敌人。使用只有聪明的小猫才会懂得利用的卡牌来创建独特的比赛。玩转洛基的不同版本，演变他的特殊能力，如同一名真正的猫战士一样参与这场战争 ^.^ <br><br>以手绘的可爱艺术风格和一丝幽默感，&quot;9 Lives to Defend&quot; 是一款有趣而具有挑战性的游戏，将考验您的战斗和策略能力。<br><br><br>• 在24或12分钟的旅行中生存下来。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389560/extras/dfadbb3af0e3a52cb1d52122a04f7302.poster.avif?t=1752182360\" width=626 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389560/extras/dfadbb3af0e3a52cb1d52122a04f7302.webm?t=1752182360\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389560/extras/dfadbb3af0e3a52cb1d52122a04f7302.mp4?t=1752182360\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>• 玩转不同版本的洛基。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389560/extras/7414b1640690b6846d30752fe2634263.poster.avif?t=1752182360\" width=608 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389560/extras/7414b1640690b6846d30752fe2634263.webm?t=1752182360\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389560/extras/7414b1640690b6846d30752fe2634263.mp4?t=1752182360\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>• 面对老板。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389560/extras/6c315afcd878dab75a7f61234079c38b.poster.avif?t=1752182360\" width=608 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389560/extras/6c315afcd878dab75a7f61234079c38b